{"tid":2075870,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"13歲童控暴動 將轉介區院與成年被告同受審 辯方反對無果","createTime":"2020-06-23T06:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T02:08:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"142a4f578c674baba5f06e9fa097535cb521fc17","tid":2075870,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/Y4UYUBXFLBYH4CMZGOZDSLFFB4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FY4UYUBXFLBYH4CMZGOZDSLFFB4%2F&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7pMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=556d7edd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200623%2FY4UYUBXFLBYH4CMZGOZDSLFFB4%2F&h=718fb169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200623/Y4UYUBXFLBYH4CMZGOZDSLFFB4/</a><br />\n<br />\n網民去年10月13日發起各區「神獸罷鷲」行動，有便衣警在將軍澳疑遭示威者私了襲擊。一名被指涉案的13歲男童被控四罪，控方早前申請將其中一項非法集結罪改控為暴動罪，今再向少年法庭申請，將案件轉介至區域法院，與其他案件合併審理。辯方反對，認為此舉會對男童做成不公。惟裁判官指法例規定少年庭並無司法管轄權處理少年犯與成人犯共同檢控的案件，控方亦有權選擇審訊的法庭。辯方不再反對，男童獲准繼續保釋，下月7日到區域法院應訊。"},{"pid":"e778065a379068e95274c430ee279564bdb3c88e","tid":2075870,"uid":241804,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92375a8b0e9dc089cfc5e356ed278c200da5a30f","tid":2075870,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:31:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7232e4b8b89a92877da550e0c95500c89417ffe1","tid":2075870,"uid":47356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T06:33:42.000Z"